## Detailed Implementation Plan: Universe Page Upgrade

### Overview of Current State

The current `Universe.jsx` at `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\src\components\Universe\Universe.jsx` is a single 366-line file containing:
- All camera logic (drag, wheel zoom, pinch zoom) inline
